.

1. *Umre* ga je pre dve nedelje. (He died two weeks ago.)
2. Otišao je da se *umre* u njegovim zemljama. (He went to die in his countries.)
3. *Umre* se posle dugog boravka u bolnici. (He died after a long stay in the hospital.)
4. Njegov brat je *umro* pre dve godine. (His brother died two years ago.)
5. Ona je *umrla* kad je imala samo 16 godina. (She died when she was only 16 years old.)
6. Otac je *umro* pre nego što je napunio 55 godina. (The father died before he was 55 years old.)